# Introduction

This is the extracted text of FM22-10 from the US Army ca 1951. I hold no copyright on the material. It is provided for the general benefit of the public in GETTING AFTER IT.

As referenced in the the Jocko Podcast # 172 available at
http://jockopodcast.com/2019/04/10/172-man-is-the-fundamental-instrument-of-war-and-that-remains-constant-army-field-manual-10-22/

# Status

This is a preliminary version and could have typos. Corrections and most welcome.

# Dedication

To those who run into danger rather than running away from it.
